Package: eva-bootstrap
Architecture: amd64
Version: 0.3.12-1
Maintainer: Andreas Mueller <amu@gnoppix.com>
Description: Eva Bootstrap Server - DHT seed for peer discovery
 Eva bootstrap server acts as a DHT seed node for peer discovery.
 Clients query this to find other peers and relay servers.
 .
 Features:
  - DNS SRV service discovery
  - Key ownership verification
  - Rate limiting and anti-abuse
Depends: libssl3
Section: net
Priority: optional